        "content": {
            "rendered": "\n<div class=\"wp-block-query is-layout-flow wp-block-query-is-layout-flow\"><ul class=\"wp-block-post-template is-layout-flow wp-block-post-template-is-layout-flow\"><li class=\"wp-block-post post-213 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-book category-review\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-post-title\">Ikigai: 10 Rules to a Fulfilling Life</h2>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-post-date\"><time datetime=\"2024-10-21T16:42:37+05:30\">October 21, 2024</time></div>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-post-excerpt\"><p class=\"wp-block-post-excerpt__excerpt\">Introduction Ikigai is a Japanese concept that translates to &#8220;reason for being.&#8221; It is the idea of finding a purpose in life that brings you joy, fulfilment, and satisfaction. The 10 rules&#8230; </p></div>\n</li><li class=\"wp-block-post post-208 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-programming category-software-development category-tutorials tag-go-environment-variables tag-go-language-tutorial tag-go-programming-basics tag-go-setup tag-golang-installation tag-hello-world-program tag-homebrew-go-installation tag-install-go-on-mac tag-mac-programming tag-simple-go-program\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-post-title\">Getting started with Go (Mac)</h2>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-post-date\"><time datetime=\"2024-06-14T13:53:59+05:30\">June 14, 2024</time></div>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-post-excerpt\"><p class=\"wp-block-post-excerpt__excerpt\">Welcome to my blog! In this post, I&#8217;ll guide you on how to set up Go (Golang) on a Mac and run a basic &#8220;Hello, world!&#8221; program. Go is an open-source, statically&#8230; </p></div>\n</li><li class=\"wp-block-post post-201 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-product-announcements category-software-updates category-tech-reviews category-technology-news tag-airpods tag-apple-innovations tag-apple-tv tag-apple-updates tag-apple-vision-pro tag-ios-18 tag-ipados-18 tag-macos-sequoia tag-product-launch tag-siri tag-software-features tag-tech-highlights tag-visionos-2 tag-watchos-11 tag-wwdc24\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-post-title\">The Apple Event 2024: A Glimpse into the Future of Technology</h2>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-post-date\"><time datetime=\"2024-06-12T11:19:19+05:30\">June 12, 2024</time></div>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-post-excerpt\"><p class=\"wp-block-post-excerpt__excerpt\">Apple&#8217;s WWDC24 event on June 10th was nothing short of spectacular, showcasing a plethora of platform updates, new features, and innovative technologies. From celebrating the 5th anniversary of Apple TV+ to introducing&#8230; </p></div>\n</li></ul>\n\n<nav class=\"wp-block-query-pagination is-layout-flex wp-block-query-pagination-is-layout-flex\" aria-label=\"Pagination\">\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-query-pagination-numbers\"><span aria-current=\"page\" class=\"page-numbers current\">1</span>\n<a class=\"page-numbers\" href=\"?query-0-page=2&#038;per_page=100&#038;page=1\">2</a>\n<a class=\"page-numbers\" href=\"?query-0-page=3&#038;per_page=100&#038;page=1\">3</a>\n<span class=\"page-numbers dots\">&hellip;</span>\n<a class=\"page-numbers\" href=\"?query-0-page=6&#038;per_page=100&#038;page=1\">6</a></div>\n\n<a href=\"/wp-json/wp/v2/pages?per_page=100&#038;page=1&#038;query-0-page=2\" class=\"wp-block-query-pagination-next\">Next Page</a>\n</nav>\n\n</div>\n",
